---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pricing — Tenz Technologies" description="Indicative pricing and commercial terms for Tenz Technologies delivery.">
  <section class="space-y-6">
    <header class="space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Flexible, transparent pricing</h1>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        We work with a variety of engagement models so you only pay for the right support at the right time.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/60 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950/40">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Retainer</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Ongoing access to technical and operational support (monthly or quarterly).</p>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
          <li>Dedicated weekly support blocks</li>
          <li>Priority planning and delivery</li>
          <li>Quarterly roadmap reviews</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">Starting at <span class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300">$6,000/mo</span></p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/60 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950/40">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Project</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Fixed-scope delivery for defined outcomes (software, process, or architecture work).</p>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
          <li>Scope & timeline alignment</li>
          <li>Milestone-based delivery</li>
          <li>Post-launch support window</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">Starts at <span class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300">$18,000</span></p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/60 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950/40">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Advisory</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Short-term strategic work: architecture reviews, technical due diligence, or planning workshops.</p>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
          <li>Rapid discovery & recommendations</li>
          <li>Executive-level deliverables</li>
          <li>Flexible scheduling</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">From <span class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300">$2,200</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/60 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950/40">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Not sure which fits?</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        Reach out and we’ll suggest the most efficient engagement model for your goals, timeline, and budget.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow hover:bg-indigo-500">Contact us</a>
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800">Schedule a call</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
